Brief
    This is a home made Google Chrome extension for that allows in one 
    click to check the weather situation in Sweden/Nordic region. The 
    weather information is provided by Swedish Meteorological and Hydrological
    Institute (SMHI, http://www.smhi.se).

    Check demo sub folder for the extension's screenshots.

Installation
    Drag and drop a .CRX file to your Google Chrome to install it. Please note 
    that you can change your region in a Options page.

Copyright
    This extension is free and could be freely modified for personal needs.
    
    To make this extension GoogleTranslate Extension was used as an example.

    Extension is using scripts and resources from http://www.smhi.se. 
